  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueBox: {fileID: 2046554254}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1577708479}
  navImg: {fileID: 190495181}
  dialogueLines:
  - In addition to teleportation being disabled on this planet,
  - It seems like we can only use a certain number of lines of code to get the gems
    in each area.
  - Looks like we're gonna have to use loops!
  - These loops can repeat code that's indented and spaced to the right.
  - I gave you some sample code that shifts me from left to right! Try and edit it
    to get the gem! Good luck cap!
  dialogueMoods:
  - thinking
  - shocked
  - 
  - 
  - happy
  sprites:
